data.description: Are you looking for a lovely 4 bedroom, 1.5 bath home, under $250,000, in Smyrna? Well search no more!! This home offers spacious living, family and dining room areas with original hardwood flooring. The kitchen, located at the rear of the home, has stainless steel appliances, large pantry and frontloading washer and dryer. Enjoy the bay window overlooking the covered brick patio and sizeable fenced yard w/ detached garage.  There are 3 bedrooms and a full hall bath, with cast iron clawfoot tub, on the second floor and another bedroom and storage area located on the third level of the home. Home is being sold AS IS, but seems to be in good condition. Delaware Street is a quiet area lined with beautiful trees and easy access to fun town events such as parades, trick or treating, Smyrna at Night and Juneteenth Celebration! The home is within walking distance to JBM Middle and Smyrna Elementary Schools, Lake Como, Smyrna Public Library and quaint shops and eateries. Make your appointment to see this home today!
